<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Inspiring Video Collection</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f4f6f8;
      color: #333;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    section {
      background: white;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    iframe {
      display: block;
      margin: 10px auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <main>
    <h1>Inspiring Video Collection</h1>
    <p>Explore a curated selection of videos designed to motivate, educate, and spark creativity.</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Creative Thinking</h2>
      <p>Learn how to unlock your creativity and approach problems from new perspectives.</p>
      <iframe 
        width="560" 
        height="315" 
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3kGx1yF1cYc" 
        title="Creative Thinking Video"
        allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Success Mindset</h2>
      <p>Discover the habits and mindset that can help you achieve your goals.</p>
      <iframe 
        width="560" 
        height="315" 
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wnHW6o8WMas" 
        title="Success Mindset Video"
        allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Learning Strategies</h2>
      <p>Improve how you learn with proven techniques backed by science.</p>
      <iframe 
        width="560" 
        height="315" 
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/O96fE1E-rf8" 
        title="Learning Strategies Video"
        allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </section>

  </main>

</body>
</html>
